docs.text: About mkdocs For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site called ./site . mkdocs gh-deploy push your document site to github pages mkdocs help - Print this help message. Tips: Add echo "site/" >> .gitignore to .gitignore file Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. theme:... Theme pip install mkdocs-material and Add it to mkdocs.yml.

docs.text: 001.两数之和 题目 nums = [2, 7, 11, 15], target = 9 代码 class Solution { public int [] twoSum ( int [] nums , int target ) { HashMap < Integer , Integer > map = new HashMap <> (); for ( int i = 0 ; i < nums . length ; i ++ ) { int temp = target - nums [ i ] ; if ( map . containsKey ( temp )) { return new int [] { i , map . get ( temp )}; } map . put ( nums [ i ] , i ); } throw new IllegalArgumentException ( "No two sum solution" ); } } 解读 陈总醍醐灌顶 002.两数相加 题目 输入：(2 -> 4 -> 3) + (5 -> 6 -> 4) 输出：7 -> 0 -> 8 原因：342 + 465 = 807 代码 class Solution { public ListNode addTwoNumbers ( ListNode l1 , ListNode l2 ) { if ( l1 == null ) return l2 ; if ( l2 == null ) return l1 ; ListNode preHead = new ListNode ( - 1 ); //创建一个新的链表必须有一个值 ListNode cur = preHead ; int sum = 0 ; while ( l1 != null || l2 != null ) { if ( l1 != null ) { sum += l1 . val ; l1 = l1 . next ; } if ( l2 != null ) { sum += l2 . val ; l2 = l2 . next ; } cur . next = new ListNode ( sum % 10 ); sum /= 10 ; cur = cur . next ; } // 这一步很重要 if ( sum == 1 ) { cur . next = new ListNode ( 1 ); } return preHead . next ; } 解读 你学废了吗
